{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id0e673993-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s9604"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"9604"},"text":"§ 9604.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Existing technical assistance providers","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary shall continue awards for the support of the Eisenhower Regional Mathematics and Science Education Consortia established under part M of the Educational Research, Development, Dissemination, and Improvement Act of 1994 (as such part existed on the day before ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-11-05"},"text":"November 5, 2002","children":[],"tail":"), the Regional Technology in Education Consortia under section 3141 of the Elementary and Secondary Education Act of 1965 (as such section existed on the day before "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-01-08"},"text":"January 8, 2002","children":[],"tail":"), and the Comprehensive Regional Assistance Centers established under part K of the Educational Research, Development, Dissemination, and Improvement Act of 1994 (as such part existed on the day before "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-11-05"},"text":"November 5, 2002","children":[],"tail":"), in accordance with the terms of such awards, until the comprehensive centers authorized under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s9602"},"text":"section 9602 of this title","children":[],"tail":" are established."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id0e673994-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/279/tII/s205"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–279, title II, § 205","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-11-05"},"text":"Nov. 5, 2002","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/116/1979"},"text":"116 Stat. 1979","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id0e673995-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id0e673996-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id0e673997-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Parts K and M of the Educational Research, Development, Dissemination, and Improvement Act of 1994 (as such parts existed on the day before ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-11-05"},"text":"November 5, 2002","children":[],"tail":"), referred to in text, mean parts K and M of title IX of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/227"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–227","children":[],"tail":", which were classified to parts G (§ 6053 et seq.) and I (§ 6055 et seq.), respectively, of subchapter IX of chapter 68 of this title, prior to repeal by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/279/tIV/s403/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–279, title IV, § 403(2)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-11-05"},"text":"Nov. 5, 2002","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/116/1985"},"text":"116 Stat. 1985","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 3141 of the Elementary and Secondary Education Act of 1965 (as such section existed on the day before ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-01-08"},"text":"January 8, 2002","children":[],"tail":"), referred to in text, is "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/10/tIII/s3141"},"text":"section 3141 of title III of Pub. L. 89–10","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/382/tI/s101"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–382, title I, § 101","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1994-10-20"},"text":"Oct. 20, 1994","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/108/3649"},"text":"108 Stat. 3649","children":[],"tail":", which was classified to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s6861"},"text":"section 6861 of this title","children":[],"tail":" prior to the general amendment of title III of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/10"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–10","children":[],"tail":" by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/110/tIII/s301"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–110, title III, § 301","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-01-08"},"text":"Jan. 8, 2002","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/115/1689"},"text":"115 Stat. 1689","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
